    "causal_summary": "Adds buildCopilotPromptArg as a sibling helper to resolveCopilotPromptArg in executor-config.ts. The helper accepts a typed CopilotTargetAuthority discriminated union and returns { argv, promptBody, enforcedPlanOnly }. Approved authority prepends a TARGET AUTHORITY preamble naming the workflow-resolved spec folder; missing authority on a write-intent dispatch replaces the prompt with a Gate-3 question and strips --allow-all-tools. Wired into both spec_kit_deep-research_auto.yaml (lines ~596-650) and spec_kit_deep-review_auto.yaml (lines ~667-720) cli-copilot dispatch blocks. Closes the v1.0.2 I1/cli-copilot 2/8 cell where cli-copilot mutated 010-phase-parent-documentation/004-retroactive-phase-parent-migration without authorization. 13 new vitest cases pass; 24 existing executor-config cases remain green; 37/37 total.",
